title: Available 2 Bed 2 Bath
posting_body: ['Austin, 78753', 'N Interstate 35', '$1604', '2 Bedroom', 'These apartments feature a living room, dining room, and a kitchen with standard appliances, standard countertops, a dishwasher, and disposal.', 'There is wood-style flooring throughout the unit.', 'This unit also features ceiling fans, window coverings, spacious closets, fireplace, central heat and air conditioning, and washer/dryer connections and private patio or balcony.', 'Short term lease options available.', 'The community amenities include a swimming pool, sundeck, outdoor grilling and picnic area, bark park, playground, fitness center, business center, clubhouse, laundry facilities, night patrol, controlled access entry, and onsite maintenance.', 'Off-street parking included or reserved available.', 'Pets welcome.', 'This apartment is a three-minute drive to US Highway 183.', 'PHOTOS ARE AN EXAMPLE OF SIMILAR UNITS WITHIN THE BUILDING, ACTUAL UNIT MAY VARY.', '***Availability and pricing is real-time, can change daily, and varies by lease term***', 'Contact Agent:', 'Dave Burroughs', 'Independent Agents Austin TX', 'show contact info', '</h', 'Follow us on Twitter @RentalBeast', 'Find us on Facebook: <URL>']
